**Resize** (Thumb):

- `Thumb` at bottom-right corner, styled as grip dots
- `DragDelta` ‚Üí `Width += e.Vector.X`, `Height += e.Vector.Y` (clamped to min 120√ó80)
- `DragCompleted` ‚Üí fire `CardResized`

