### Snap-to-Grid Logic

In `CanvasDashboardViewModel.OnCardDropped()`:

```csharp
if (!IsSnapToGridEnabled) return;
card.PositionX = Math.Round(card.PositionX / GridSize) * GridSize;
card.PositionY = Math.Round(card.PositionY / GridSize) * GridSize;
// Property change ‚Üí Canvas.Left/Top transition animates the snap (150ms)
```

